cat("Greetings from Earth. After years of speculations, we are both glad and terrified to meet intelligent extraterrestrials. Hopefully, by the time this message reaches you and you meet the human race, we would have become more welcoming towards other beings. I hope that instead of getting involved in meaningless conflicts, we can prosper together. Also, if you do visit us, please don't visit us in the year 2020. I don't think we could handle extraterrestrials on top of everything this year. :)")
